channel.title: 718/728 Black Screen
channel.description:
It's all perfect and running smoothly, Most bosses is fine! But when i go to things like Nex, Bandos, Armadyl ect... It black screens?
The server was previously a 718/742 but i switched it over to 728.
Anyone have any idea what's happening??

item.title: 718/728 Black Screen
item.dc:creator: @PrecisionXdefy PrecisionXdefy
item.description:
@PrecisionXdefy wrote:

This may be a problem if you have changed the cache and the source files are set to a certain cache , if everyone is having the problem try running in openGL and use commands displayfps in game and wait till the cache reaches 100%

hope it helps

PrecisionXdefy
